OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FA Cumbrian MP has become the first
OL,7,FLabour MP to speak out against the UK
OL,8,FGovernment's changes to inheritance
OL,9,Ftax for farms.
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has faced
OL,12,FLabour pressure to amend her
OL,13,Finheritance tax changes for farmers as
OL,14,Fa backbencher made clear his
OL,15,Fopposition to the current proposals.
