OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FMarkus Campbell-Savours, the Labour MP
OL,7,Ffor Penrith and Solway, said he is
OL,8,F"not prepared to break my word" given
OL,9,Fto farmers during the election that
OL,10,FLabour had no plans to introduce
OL,11,Fchanges to agricultural property
OL,12,Frelief (APR).
OL,14,FHe said he will engage with the
OL,15,FTreasury and Department for
OL,16,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,17,F(Defra) over the coming months and
OL,18,F"seek important amendments", telling
OL,19,Fthe Commons: "If today was the real
OL,20,Fvote I would vote against the
OL,21,FGovernment's plans."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/17
