OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FMr Campbell-Savours went on to
OL,7,Fcriticise the Conservatives for
OL,8,Ftabling a motion calling for the
OL,9,Fpolicy to be axed, saying it failed to
OL,10,Facknowledge "how they failed to
OL,11,Fdeliver for my farmers".
OL,13,FUnder measures announced at the
OL,14,FBudget, farmers will pay a rate of 20%
OL,15,Finheritance tax on agricultural
OL,16,Fproperty and land worth more than #1
OL,17,Fmillion when they previously paid none.
OL,19,FThere is a higher threshold of #3
OL,20,Fmillion for couples passing on their
OL,21,Ffarms.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/17
