OL,6,FThe Treasury says around 500 estates a
OL,7,Fyear are expected to pay inheritance
OL,8,Ftax under the changes, but shadow
OL,9,Fenvironment secretary Victoria Atkins
OL,10,Fcast doubt on the numbers and
OL,11,Fcriticised the Chancellor's "cock-eyed
OL,12,Faccounting" as she opened an
OL,13,FOpposition Day Debate in the Commons.
