OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "Our
OL,7,Fcommitment to farmers remains
OL,8,Fsteadfast ` we have committed #5
OL,9,Fbillion to the farming budget over two
OL,10,Fyears, including more money than ever
OL,11,Ffor sustainable food production, and
OL,12,Fwe are developing a 25-year farming
OL,13,Froadmap, focusing on how to make the
OL,14,Fsector more profitable in the decades
OL,15,Fto come.
