OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,F"Our reform to Agricultural and
OL,7,FBusiness Property Relief will impact
OL,8,Faround 500 estates a year. For these
OL,9,Festates, inheritance tax will be at
OL,10,Fhalf the rate paid by others, with 10
OL,11,Fyears to pay the liability back
OL,12,Finterest free. This is a fair and
OL,13,Fbalanced approach which fixes the
OL,14,Fpublic services we all rely on."
