OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FThe Conservative non-binding motion
OL,7,Fsaid figures from the National
OL,8,FFarmers' Union suggest that "some
OL,9,Fthree-quarters of farms will be
OL,10,Faffected" while the Central
OL,11,FAssociation of Agricultural Valuers
OL,12,Fanticipates the policy "will affect
OL,13,F75,000 owners of farming businesses
OL,14,Fover a generation".
