OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FMr Campbell-Savours told the debate:
OL,7,F"I've spent the last few weeks
OL,8,Fspeaking with farmers in Penrith and
OL,9,FSolway, trying to understand the full
OL,10,Fimpact of the inheritance tax
OL,11,Fproposals knowing that I have months
OL,12,Fleft to engage Defra and the Treasury
OL,13,Fand seek important amendments.
OL,15,F"And, let me be clear, if today was
OL,16,Fthe real vote I would vote against the
OL,17,FGovernment's plans.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/17
