OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,F"I'm no rebel, I'm a moderate. But
OL,7,Fduring the election I read what I
OL,8,Fthought were assurances from my party
OL,9,Fthat we had no plans to introduce
OL,10,Fchanges to APR.
OL,12,FOn this basis I reassured farmers in
OL,13,Fmy constituency that we would not.
OL,14,FNow, I'm simply not prepared to break
OL,15,Fmy word.
OL,17,F"I'm told that there is no Labour MP
OL,18,Fin the country with as many farms as I
OL,19,Fhave in Penrith and Solway and I hope
OL,20,Fmy colleagues will understand my
OL,21,Ffeelings on this.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
