OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,F"Today, however, we're debating a
OL,7,Ffrankly irrelevant motion from the
OL,8,FConservative Party, a motion which
OL,9,Ffails to acknowledge how they failed
OL,10,Fto deliver for my farmers."
OL,12,FMr Campbell-Savours said the
OL,13,FConservatives failed in several areas,
OL,14,Fincluding on the need to reform
OL,15,Finheritance tax rules that "farmers
OL,16,Fknow were being abused by non-farmers
OL,17,Fat their expense".
OL,19,FHe said: "I simply won't walk into a
OL,20,Flobby with people who talk a good game
OL,21,Fon farming but don't deliver."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/17
