OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FShe said: "Before ambitious
OL,7,Fbackbenchers, or indeed (Treasury
OL,8,Fminister James Murray), get to their
OL,9,Ffeet and accuse these farmers and us
OL,10,Fof scaremongering - something they've
OL,11,Fbeen happy to do in the past - think
OL,12,Fon, discover some humility and
OL,13,Fcompassion and ask why tens of
OL,14,Fthousands of decent, hard-working and
OL,15,Fsensible people across the United
OL,16,FKingdom know that the Chancellor has
OL,17,Fgot it so wrong."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/17
