OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FMs Atkins added on farmers: "They feed
OL,7,Fus and now they need us. Labour MPs
OL,8,Fneed to join us and axe the family
OL,9,Ffarm tax."
OL,11,FThe Government tabled an amendment
OL,12,Fthat stated the Government has to
OL,13,F"make difficult decisions to protect
OL,14,Ffarms and farmers in the context of
OL,15,Fthe #22 billion fiscal black hole"
OL,16,Fleft by the previous Conservative
OL,17,Fgovernment.
