OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FIt added: "Under the changes announced
OL,7,Fin the Budget around three quarters of
OL,8,Fclaims for agricultural property
OL,9,Frelief, including those that also
OL,10,Fclaim business property relief, are
OL,11,Fexpected to not pay more inheritance
OL,12,Ftax."
OL,14,FSpeaking in the debate, Treasury
OL,15,Fminister Mr Murray declined to be
OL,16,Fdrawn on whether the Treasury would
OL,17,Fconsider a U-turn on the policy in
OL,18,Ffuture if data shows the Government
OL,19,Fmade a mistake.
