OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FOn how many farmers might be affected
OL,7,Fby the agricultural property relief on
OL,8,Finheritance tax, Mr Murray said: "It
OL,9,Fis not possible to accurately infer a
OL,10,Ffuture inheritance tax liability from
OL,11,Fdata on farm asset values.
OL,13,F"Any inheritance tax liabilities that
OL,14,Ffarming assets may face would be
OL,15,Faffected by who the owners are, the
OL,16,Fnature of ownership, how many owners
OL,17,Fthere are, any borrowing they have,
OL,18,Fand how they've planned their affairs."
