OL,3,CCumbrian MP first to speak out against
OL,4,Cgovernment changes to inheritance tax
OL,6,FMr Murray replied: "When we approach
OL,7,Fpolicies in Government, we thoroughly
OL,8,Ftest them and consider the detail of
OL,9,Fthat policy. We consider the data of
OL,10,Fthat policy and we make sure that any
OL,11,Fconclusions we draw are based on the
OL,12,Fcorrect set of data."
OL,14,FMPs rejected the Conservative motion
OL,15,Fby 339 votes to 181, majority 158.
OL,17,FThe Government amendment was accepted
OL,18,Fwithout the need for a formal vote.
